                <p>Write tests in the multiple-choice questions (MCQs) format</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 text-center">
                <h3>Practice</h3>
                <p>Take tests and monitor your progress over time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 text-center">
                <h3>Share</h3>
                <p>Send tests to your colleagues or find tests created by others</p>
            </div>
        </div>
